      <title>春日赏梅</title>
      <link href="/2019/03/12/poem-plumblossom/"/>
      <url>/2019/03/12/poem-plumblossom/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>雨歇风住春色满<br>偶得无瑕小阳天<br>寻至新梅满园处<br>赏尽英华不欲归</p></blockquote><img src="/2019/03/12/poem-plumblossom/1.jpg" title="[凡间红霞]"><img src="/2019/03/12/poem-plumblossom/2.jpg" title="[孤枝芳华]"><img src="/2019/03/12/poem-plumblossom/3.jpg" title="[艳中少女]"><img src="/2019/03/12/poem-plumblossom/4.jpg" title="[临湖粉黛]">]]></content>
      
      
